Package com.alexkasko.unsafe.offheap

Interface Summary
OffHeapAddressable Basic interface for off-heap long-indexed collections.
OffHeapDisposable Basic interface for off-heap classes that support manual memory freeing.
OffHeapLongAddressable Interface for off-heap collections with long elements.
OffHeapPayloadAddressable Interface for off-heap header-payload collection.
OffHeapPayloadIntAddressable Interface for off-heap header-int_payload collection.
OffHeapPayloadLongAddressable Interface for off-heap header-long_payload collection.
 

Class Summary
LongPacker Contains static methods for packing two values with limited size (one long and one int) into one long value.
OffHeapBinarySearch Binary search implementation borrowed from https://android.googlesource.com/platform/libcore/+/android-4.2.2_r1/luni/src/main/java/java/util/Arrays.java and adapted to OffHeapAddressable
OffHeapBinarySearch.IndexRange OffHeapAddressable index range representation.
OffHeapLongArray Implementation of array of long using OffHeapMemory.
OffHeapLongArrayList Implementation of array-list of long using OffHeapMemory.

OffHeapMemory Allocates an area of off-heap memory that is not a subject to GC.
OffHeapPayloadArray Implementation of off-heap header-payload array.
OffHeapPayloadArrayList Implementation of off-heap header-payload array-list of long using OffHeapMemory.
OffHeapPayloadIntArray Implementation of off-heap header-int_payload array.

OffHeapPayloadLongArrayList Implementation of off-heap header-long_payload array-list of long using OffHeapMemory.
